title: Is Kristin The Only Person That Does This In Her Car?
description:
Sometimes, you just need a good scream release to let out ALL the frustration that's been building up over the past few weeks or months. Kristin has these moments in her car, and Bert can't believe it. Is Kristin the only person that does this?
